                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-sky-700 mb-4">Welcome Elektro Students!</h2>
                <p class="mb-3">This interactive guide will help you understand Generative Artificial Intelligence (AI). We'll explore what it is, how it works, its dangers, and how it can be a useful tool for you, especially in your Elektro studies. This course is designed to be practical and help you improve your English too!</p>
                <p class="mb-3"><strong>Course Overview:</strong> This guide is based on a seven-session course. We'll cover:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4 space-y-1">
                    <li>What AI and Generative AI are.</li>
                    <li>How Large Language Models (LLMs) like ChatGPT learn and create text.</li>
                    <li>Understanding AI "hallucinations" ‚Äì when AI makes mistakes.</li>
                    <li>The dangers of AI: misinformation, deepfakes, bias, and how AI can affect our thinking.</li>
                    <li>Ethical issues like plagiarism and data privacy.</li>
                    <li>How AI can help you with brainstorming and improving your own work.</li>
                    <li>The impact of AI on technical jobs, including Elektro.</li>
                    <li>Thinking about rules for using AI responsibly.</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Click on the navigation buttons above to explore the different modules. Let's start learning!</p>
            </div>
